task.summary: Refactoring. ColorBaseConveter class to be responsible for conversions.

Renamed filters to filterDelegates to make distinction between ColorBaseFilter subclasses that encapsulate function parameters as well
Added type safety for parsing object and strings to doubles
Constant regex pattern for hex colorBase patterns for easier pattern writing
